PN,38101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FA hosepipe ban has been extended to
OL,7,Finclude more than two million South
OL,8,FEast Water customers in Sussex,
OL,9,FSurrey, Hampshire and Berkshire.
OL,11,FThe company said the restrictions are
OL,12,Fbeing brought in from Saturday amid
OL,13,Fthe recent hot weather conditions.
OL,15,FSouth East Water are asking customers
OL,16,Fto cut back water use straight away,
OL,17,Ftelling them not to use hosepipes for
OL,18,Ftheir gardens, cars, patios, boats or
OL,19,Fswimming pools.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FThe ban had previously been in place
OL,7,Fjust for its customers in Kent.
OL,9,FThe firm said it has seen a "decline
OL,10,Fin river levels" and needs to "protect
OL,11,Fsome groundwater sources" after lower
OL,12,Fthan average rainfall, hot weather and
OL,13,Fhigh demand for water.
OL,15,FDouglas Whitfield, water supply
OL,16,Fdirector at South East Water, said:
OL,17,F"Our absolute priority has to be
OL,18,Fmaking sure there is always enough
OL,19,Fwater for everyone's essential daily
OL,20,Fneeds: drinking, cooking and hygiene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,F"To safeguard our shared resource and
OL,7,Fhelp prevent any homes from facing a
OL,8,Fsudden loss of water, we sadly need to
OL,9,Fask our communities to not use their
OL,10,Fhosepipes immediately.
OL,12,F"We are deeply sorry for the
OL,13,Fdisruption this causes, and we are
OL,14,Fincredibly grateful to everyone
OL,15,Fhelping us protect water supplies in
OL,16,FSussex, Surrey, Hampshire and
OL,17,FBerkshire."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FThe temporary restrictions will be in
OL,7,Fforce from 00.01 on Saturday, 25 July,
OL,8,Fhowever the company is asking
OL,9,Fcustomers in Sussex, Surrey, Hampshire
OL,10,Fand Berkshire to follow the rules of
OL,11,Fthe ban immediately.
OL,13,FThis will mean that customers should
OL,14,Fnot use hosepipes for watering their
OL,15,Fgardens, washing cars, patios and
OL,16,Fboats and for filling swimming and
OL,17,Fpaddling pools.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FSouth East Water says it's not had to
OL,7,Fplace a temporary restriction in
OL,8,FSurrey, Hampshire and Berkshire in 14
OL,9,Fyears, since 2012.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, for customers in Sussex
OL,12,Fthis is the fourth hosepipe ban they
OL,13,Fwill have experienced in five years.
OL,15,FIt comes as central and south-east
OL,16,FEngland have seen the longest unbroken
OL,17,Fspell of no recorded rainfall this
OL,18,Fcentury, Met Office figures suggest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FAn average of zero rainfall has been
OL,7,Fmeasured across the organisation's
OL,8,Fweather stations in both regions for
OL,9,F14 days in a row, from July 2 to July
OL,10,F15, according to the latest available
OL,11,Fdata.
OL,13,FThis is the longest unbroken run of
OL,14,Fdays with no rain for south-east
OL,15,FEngland since a 15-day spell in April
OL,16,F1997.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FReservoir storage levels in England
OL,7,Fare currently at 79%, around five
OL,8,Fpercentage points below the long-term
OL,9,Faverage for the time of year, the
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency said as it released
OL,11,Fits weekly dry weather and drought
OL,12,Freport on Friday.
OL,14,FSix reservoirs are classed as having
OL,15,F"notably low" levels, including
OL,16,FWimbleball in Somerset, Grafham in
OL,17,FCambridgeshire and Hanningfield in
OL,18,FEssex, while Blagdon reservoir in
OL,19,FSomerset is classed as being
OL,20,F"exceptionally low".
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FIt comes after there have been 28 days
OL,7,Fin 2026, consecutive and non-
OL,8,Fconsecutive, when 30C has been
OL,9,Fexceeded somewhere in the UK: seven in
OL,10,FMay, eight in June and 13 in July.
OL,12,FThe record for the number of 30C-plus
OL,13,Fdays in a calendar year is 34, which
OL,14,Fwas set in 1995.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,FDr Jess Neumann, associate professor
OL,7,Fin hydrology, University of Reading
OL,8,Fsaid: "Hosepipe bans are
OL,9,Funderstandably unpopular with
OL,10,Fcustomers. At a time when there is
OL,11,Fgrowing pressure on water companies to
OL,12,Finvest in critical infrastructure, fix
OL,13,Fleaks, and improve their overall water
OL,14,Fmanagement, many householders feel
OL,15,Fthat they are the ones being unfairly
OL,16,Fpenalised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784546294
OL,3,CHosepipe ban extended to include 2.4m
OL,4,Cpeople amid ongoing hot weather
OL,6,F"Positively, hosepipe bans do help to
OL,7,Fraise awareness of our water situation
OL,8,Fand encourage people to be more
OL,9,Fmindful of their everyday water use.
OL,10,FThey also help reduce pressure on our
OL,11,Frivers and the wildlife that depend on
OL,12,Fnatural water courses.
OL,14,F"Small actions such as tending to
OL,15,Fgardens with a watering can, watering
OL,16,Fless regularly, catching cold water to
OL,17,Fuse in pans and kettles whilst you
OL,18,Fwait for hot water to run in your
OL,19,Fhouse, taking shorter showers and
OL,20,Fleaving your lawn to go brown will all
OL,21,Fhelp."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
